WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.480 --> 00:00:02.133
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:02.133 --> 00:00:05.189
Thank you for joining us again today.

00:00:05.634 --> 00:00:10.416
We're going to go over some of the news that's going on in the world right now.

00:00:10.416 --> 00:00:16.880
I told Braden, I said, "Every single day there's something new of all the signs of the times.

00:00:16.880 --> 00:00:20.800
" You know, I just think it's amazing where we are.

00:00:20.800 --> 00:00:27.269
And I want to say this, how important it is that you're led by the spirit of God in your own personal life.

00:00:27.269 --> 00:00:40.320
Every single day hearing him, every single day having fellowship with him, that you are abiding in him and his words are remaining in you.

00:00:40.320 --> 00:00:42.239
Make sure you're getting in that Bible.

00:00:42.239 --> 00:00:48.027
Make sure you're getting in the word of God more than you are even on a YouTube channel or following somebody else.

00:00:48.027 --> 00:00:49.919
I hear so many different people.

00:00:49.919 --> 00:00:54.506
Well, you know, I'll just say what the Lord said today as I was praying.

00:00:54.506 --> 00:01:11.520
I was out and I was working, and he said there's so many people that used to visit him every single day, big ministers that have huge platforms that haven't had a fresh word from God in a long time.

00:01:11.520 --> 00:01:21.200
And he said upon their door, upon the arch of their door is the word Ichabod.

00:01:21.200 --> 00:01:26.400
Many of them have had an Ichabod in their ministry.

00:01:26.400 --> 00:01:34.960
And there's a lot of people that are being led by people who haven't had a fresh word from God in a long time.

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:37.079
They're living off a stale manna.

00:01:37.680 --> 00:01:39.611
They're living off a stale word.

00:01:39.611 --> 00:01:51.394
And this is concerning the prophetic and a lot of—and I always say a lot of the elders—this is happening a lot with a lot of the people that are not being in the river.

00:01:51.394 --> 00:02:01.679
They're getting a stale word and the Lord said they are upset about the words that you're getting and the words that I'm warning about to pray about.

00:02:02.435 --> 00:02:06.017
And I want to say this right off: there's so many new faces.

00:02:06.017 --> 00:02:11.504
I had over—I don't know how many thousand people in the month of May join us.

00:02:11.504 --> 00:02:14.952
I think it was like four or five thousand new faces.

00:02:14.952 --> 00:02:19.440
And so I want to say this right off the bat.

00:02:19.440 --> 00:02:21.376
I don't label myself a prophet.

00:02:21.376 --> 00:02:23.040
I'm not a self-proclaimed prophet.

00:02:23.040 --> 00:02:27.080
There's a lot of people that want to label me and say, "Brandon, you're a prophet.

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:27.480
You're this.

00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:27.1000
You're that.

00:02:27.1000 --> 00:02:32.560
" I have not had anybody ordain me as a prophet and say, "You're a prophet of God.

00:02:32.560 --> 00:02:33.519
You're this or that.

00:02:33.519 --> 00:02:37.599
" You know, I just stay in my lane.

00:02:37.599 --> 00:02:40.089
This is what the Lord did say.

00:02:40.089 --> 00:02:49.280
He said, "I want you to go on YouTube and I want you to pray and I want you to bring forth a prayer army of a million people.

00:02:49.280 --> 00:02:56.960
And in doing so, I will show you things as a watchman on the wall of that which is to come.

00:02:56.960 --> 00:03:00.539
And you will pray and you will change things.

00:03:00.539 --> 00:03:05.647
And I want you to call your church, this online church, Prayer Changes Things.

00:03:05.647 --> 00:03:06.703
That's my foundation.

00:03:06.703 --> 00:03:12.662
" The Prayer Changes Things foundation—it's not a foundation, it's the foundation of prayer.

00:03:12.662 --> 00:03:16.813
And that's why we brought it forth to say call it a prayer foundation.

00:03:16.813 --> 00:03:22.496
You must have a prayer foundation in your life in these last days.

00:03:22.496 --> 00:03:25.760
A foundation of prayer.

00:03:25.760 --> 00:03:30.480
And raising up a million men and women to pray every single day.

00:03:30.480 --> 00:03:31.280
We try.

00:03:31.280 --> 00:03:35.629
I have other things I'm doing and we really do try to bank it every day.

00:03:35.629 --> 00:03:39.280
I do get breaks and I have to feed myself spiritually.

00:03:39.280 --> 00:03:40.860
You dump out and dump out and dump out.

00:03:41.310 --> 00:03:43.760
Two hours a night, two and a half hours is a lot.

00:03:43.760 --> 00:03:49.440
But we're growing and a lot of people don't know who I am.

00:03:49.440 --> 00:03:57.119
And so I just keep trying to make that clear to everybody that I feel that my job as a watchman is to bring forth things.

00:03:57.119 --> 00:04:03.531
The Lord shows me to pray for it, and I feel our main mission is America a lot.

00:04:03.531 --> 00:04:06.493
People are upset: "Brandon, please pray for Africa.

00:04:06.493 --> 00:04:08.147
Please pray for Australia.

00:04:08.147 --> 00:04:14.400
" When the Lord puts it on my heart to pray for it, my primary focus right now is to get President Trump across the finish line.

00:04:14.400 --> 00:04:24.753
I know we have a population of only 340 million people and there's billions more people out there, but God will raise up more prayer people in those nations.

00:04:24.753 --> 00:04:31.030
I truly believe there's other prayer people that God is raising up that just haven't been obedient to what he's asked them to do.

00:04:31.030 --> 00:04:35.360
He didn't leave your nation without prayer warriors.

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:37.860
God said, "Brandon, I want you to pray for President Trump.

00:04:37.860 --> 00:04:50.000
" And I have a lot of words concerning President Trump to pray for him, concerning his health, concerning his mental well-being, concerning demonic attacks against him.

00:04:50.000 --> 00:04:53.280
So, if it comes across as I have a lot of words, that's because that's my assignment.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:53.760
What's your assignment?

00:04:54.719 --> 00:04:56.022
You stick to your assignment.

00:04:56.022 --> 00:04:58.790
If you don't want to pray for America, I pray for America.

00:04:58.790 --> 00:04:59.710
I pray for Canada.

00:04:59.710 --> 00:05:00.693
I pray for Mexico.

00:05:00.693 --> 00:05:01.867
I pray for Brazil.

00:05:01.867 --> 00:05:03.600
I pray for South America.

00:05:03.600 --> 00:05:06.769
I feel I'm called—you've noticed I've prayed for everybody.

00:05:06.769 --> 00:05:11.620
But my main focus is to make sure President Trump makes his mission.

00:05:11.620 --> 00:05:18.800
And right now, I told you that 25th Amendment was what they were after.

00:05:18.800 --> 00:05:22.720
They want to overthrow him with a coup.

00:05:22.720 --> 00:05:27.662
And the Lord said, "Pray for him to make it across the finish line concerning his term.

00:05:27.662 --> 00:05:31.070
For they will try to throw him out before it's over.

00:05:31.070 --> 00:05:40.674
If they don't take him out with a pow-pow or some kind of event, they will try to do the 25th Amendment: He's not fit for office.

00:05:40.674 --> 00:05:47.839
" And today, every single thing I see—look how he's fallen asleep at the New York Knicks game.

00:05:47.839 --> 00:05:51.660
Well, maybe the Knicks game was boring, you know?

00:05:51.660 --> 00:05:51.850
I don't know.

00:05:52.230 --> 00:06:07.319
Oh, he's falling asleep and everybody's upset saying he needs—this guy, he made fun of Sleepy Joe and now he's not fit for office anymore because he's falling asleep and they're just ridiculing him all over the place today and he needs to be investigated.

00:06:07.319 --> 00:06:09.600
This is what I told you was coming.

00:06:09.600 --> 00:06:14.760
What the spirit of the Lord said, he said the 25th Amendment, they're going to try to use it in the days ahead.

00:06:14.760 --> 00:06:16.301
They're really going to try to work on this.

00:06:16.301 --> 00:06:23.280
And this is why it's so vital for the elections concerning November.

00:06:23.280 --> 00:06:28.080
If we do not maintain the House and the Senate, he's in trouble.

00:06:28.080 --> 00:06:30.107
The Lord said it.

00:06:30.107 --> 00:06:34.800
And so I saw us losing the Senate.

00:06:34.800 --> 00:06:37.040
I saw us keeping the House.

00:06:37.040 --> 00:06:39.874
I saw us losing the Senate by three seats.

00:06:39.874 --> 00:06:52.560
I still keep praying over these three seats that they will flip Democrat and I'm praying over that we'll have a fair election.

00:06:52.560 --> 00:07:10.000
But if we do not get out and vote and vote with a God mentality, a God-inspired Bible-based mentality of our candidates—not voting for, "Well, they have social programs and they have this and that.

00:07:10.000 --> 00:07:10.270
" No.

00:07:10.540 --> 00:07:12.160
How do they stand on abortion?

00:07:12.160 --> 00:07:14.880
How do they stand on homosexuality?

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:18.479
How do they stand on things that are unbiblical?

00:07:18.479 --> 00:07:19.919
That's what you need to be looking at.

00:07:20.257 --> 00:07:21.271
How are they?

00:07:21.271 --> 00:07:25.017
I would say a lot with abortion and things like that.

00:07:25.017 --> 00:07:25.920
How do they vote?

00:07:26.666 --> 00:07:27.399
What do they speak?

00:07:28.119 --> 00:07:29.359
What do they say?

00:07:29.359 --> 00:07:30.533
That's what I mean.

00:07:30.533 --> 00:07:32.479
And so people say, "You get too political.

00:07:32.479 --> 00:07:34.280
" Yes, it's a political year.

00:07:34.280 --> 00:07:36.480
This is a very important year.

00:07:36.480 --> 00:07:49.555
2027, you won't hear me talk about politics as much, but I know in my heart how serious this election is concerning 2026 and 2028.

00:07:49.555 --> 00:07:56.679
When I was out and I was listening to the Holy Spirit today, I was just praying.

00:07:56.679 --> 00:08:01.111
"For those that are led by the spirit of God are the sons of God.

00:08:01.111 --> 00:08:07.449
" And if you are a child of the most high God, you are led by the spirit of God.

00:08:07.449 --> 00:08:10.926
He will lead you and he will guide you here.

00:08:10.926 --> 00:08:12.023
Romans 8.

00:08:25.280 --> 00:08:25.460
You need to know this.

00:08:25.460 --> 00:08:32.479
"For as many as are led by the spirit of God, they are the sons of God.

00:08:36.080 --> 00:08:40.756
" So if you're led by his spirit, he's going to talk to you every day.

00:08:46.830 --> 00:08:48.450
If you're not hearing the Holy Spirit on your life circumstances, on everyday issues, you're not being led by him.

00:09:00.391 --> 00:09:00.702
So, if you are led by the spirit of God, how can you be led by somebody you only hear once a month?

00:09:00.702 --> 00:09:07.291
You're not being led by the spirit of God if you only hear him once every year.

00:09:07.291 --> 00:09:11.027
You're led by the spirit of God.

00:09:11.027 --> 00:09:18.029
For those that are led by the spirit of God are the sons and daughters of God.

00:09:25.720 --> 00:09:25.980
You know you're his whenever he's talking to you.

00:09:25.980 --> 00:09:30.514
So you need to be listening to him on every area and every issue of your life.

00:09:30.514 --> 00:09:32.205
"Well, I don't know, Brandon.

00:09:32.205 --> 00:09:33.577
I never hear.

00:09:33.577 --> 00:09:36.253
" I would check my thermostat.

00:09:36.253 --> 00:09:38.182
Check your spiritual thermostat.

00:09:38.182 --> 00:09:40.720
Where are you with the Lord?

00:09:40.720 --> 00:09:44.800
How much are you spending time with Him?

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:55.449
You know, if I only spent time every couple of days or every other day with Diana, my wife, and we didn't have any intimacy—we didn't talk, we didn't have anything, just, 'Hey, how are you doing?

00:09:55.449 --> 00:09:58.080
Bye, see you later'—you're not going to have a good relationship.

00:09:59.280 --> 00:10:08.194
But when you're in love with somebody and you're in hot pursuit of her like you were when you were dating, don't let that fire burn out, gentlemen.

00:10:08.194 --> 00:10:11.000
Pursue your wife like you did when you were dating her.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.343
Pursue her.

00:10:17.657 --> 00:10:20.959
Don't say, 'Well, I have her now, I don't have to pursue her anymore.

00:10:20.959 --> 00:10:25.200
' I pursue my wife all the time.

