I said, 'Let's put on some music.

00:10:36.034 --> 00:10:37.720
Let's dance in the foyer.

00:10:37.720 --> 00:10:40.987
' And she just goes, 'You want to dance?

00:10:40.987 --> 00:10:45.200
' I said, 'Yeah, we have to make time to dance.

00:10:45.200 --> 00:10:46.846
Let's just dance together.

00:10:46.846 --> 00:10:49.360
' And she looked at me.

00:10:49.360 --> 00:10:53.279
But that's just me; I think about things.

00:10:53.279 --> 00:10:55.940
How do you make it fresh?

00:10:55.940 --> 00:10:56.960
What's dance?

