00:11:11.669 --> 00:11:19.090
But I try to create an atmosphere of love, even if it's just not there.

00:11:19.090 --> 00:11:25.386
How do you do that in a relationship with the Lord?

00:11:25.386 --> 00:11:26.839
'I feel dry today.

00:11:26.839 --> 00:11:31.130
I don't know.

00:11:31.130 --> 00:11:32.079
' No, no, no.

00:11:32.079 --> 00:11:33.360
