00:11:38.022 --> 00:11:40.280
What's coming through your eye gates?

00:11:40.280 --> 00:11:41.680
Are you watching filth?

00:11:41.680 --> 00:11:45.324
Are you watching things that grieve Him?

00:11:45.324 --> 00:11:48.222
Are you meditating on things that grieve Him?

00:11:48.222 --> 00:11:53.499
Are you scrolling on social media all day instead of spending time with Him?

00:11:53.499 --> 00:11:56.660
Take time to sit at the feet of Jesus every day.

00:11:56.660 --> 00:11:58.960
I'm talking in your spirit: 'I'm here.

00:12:03.556 --> 00:12:03.804
I want You.

00:12:05.458 --> 00:12:05.787
I need You.

00:12:05.787 --> 00:12:15.040
' I don't care what you're doing—if you're pulling weeds, if you're cleaning your car—spend time with Him.

00:12:15.040 --> 00:12:19.547
As many as are led by the Spirit of God, they are the sons and daughters of God.

00:12:19.547 --> 00:12:27.180
So you know when you're led by the Spirit because He's going to talk to you.

