00:15:18.940 --> 00:15:19.410
The Lord said, 'In two years, everything's going to look really, really different, Brandon.

00:15:34.160 --> 00:15:34.617
And in the natural, if you don't teach them how to dip in the river, this is going to be a time of sorrows.

00:15:34.617 --> 00:15:38.959
